Comment: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:22.88,Sign,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Aozora Network!\N★Hello Everybody, this is the Blue Sky Network!\NThis is a computer network created for elementary school students.\NEveryone, have fun!\N★Board Information: Click on the name of the business you want to visit!\N1. Music lovers, let's have fun together!\N2. Come together! Sports-loving club \N3. Sci-fi lovers, let's introduce our favorite books!\N4. Leave it to us for all your gaming needs!\N5. Fun manga stories, as always!\N6. Mystery Club {not sure what half of that means, and the video is too shitty to read; feel free to ignore tbh}{◆ようこそ、あおぞらネットワークへ!\N★Hello Everybody this is the Blue Sky Network!\Nここは、小学生の方達の為に作られたパソコン通信ネットです\Nみなさん。楽しんでいって下さいね\N★ボード情報 行きたい柄の商号を押してね!\N1 音楽が大好きな方、一緒に楽しもうね!\N2 集まれ!スポーツ大好き入間\N3 SF好きな人、お気に入りの本紹介\N4 ゲームのことならおまかせ\N5 やっぱり楽しいマンガの話\N6 不思議クラブ}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.45,0:00:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.22,0:00:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The story you're about to watch \Nis a strange tale that happened at a school.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.55,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who'll run into this mystery
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.08,0:00:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,are three close friends—\NRyota, Mina, and Manabu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota loves sports.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.82,0:00:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not too fond of studying, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.35,0:00:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina's a lively girl who can \Nhold her own against the boys. {mina means "everyone"}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.35,0:00:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's got a kind heart, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:48.35,0:00:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And Manabu-kun may not be great at sports, \Nbut he's a top student and the class rep. {manabu means "to study" - dunno if their names are supposed to be "talking names" or I'm just overthinking}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.22,0:01:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the story of those three as they face strange happenings at their elementary school.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.15,0:01:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So stick around for {\i1}School Ghost Stories{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:03.72,0:01:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Episode 1,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.88,0:01:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tale of the Poison Spider{\i0}, begins.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.35,0:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This mysterious event started on the day of the closing ceremony, right before summer break.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.55,0:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, your long-awaited\Nsummer vacation starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.68,0:01:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't see each other for a little while,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.45,0:01:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,so make sure you stay healthy \Nand keep a good routine. {lit: regular; well-regulated; systematic; orderly life}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.78,0:01:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we finish, there's \Nsomething important you need to know.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.62,0:01:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've heard it on the news \Nor read about it in the paper,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.62,0:01:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but last week a poisonous spider was found \Nat an elementary school in the neighboring town.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.98,0:02:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully, there haven't been any reports \Nof one near Midori Elementary yet. {this school}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.65,0:02:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you see one, \Ndon't ever try to touch it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.32,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell your mom or dad right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.85,0:02:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, let's start cleaning up the classroom and the teachers' room before the break.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.25,0:02:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Class reps, come see me after your room's done.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.18,0:02:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run away like usual \Nwhen we clean the staff room, can you? {probably means that usually they only clean the staff room and ryota always skips it?}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.52,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now wipe down these desks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.08,0:02:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I heard the kid at that other school, the one who got bitten by the spider, is still in the hospital!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, no way.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.65,0:03:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, I didn't hear it directly, \Nbut they say one showed up at our school too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.32,0:03:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.48,0:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl from Class 6-2 said she saw a huge \Nspider shadow in the corridor after club practice.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.08,0:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.48,0:03:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it? If one that big really existed, \Nthat'd be awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it called again, \Nthat poisonous spider?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Something… "back-spider"? {gokegumo = widow spider; Seakagokegumo = redback spider }
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, "Backstabbing Spider" or something? {ikazugoke = old maid; spinster - has nothing to do with spiders but ends with goke, so he connected it with gokegumo = widow spider}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was "Redback Spider."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.02,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Redback Spider."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They live in hot regions \Nlike Australia, India, and Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.92,0:03:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're venomous—if you get bitten, \Nyou might convulse, but you'll recover in a few weeks.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.85,0:03:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not aggressive, and they don't bite unless you grab them with your bare hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.75,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true professor's kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.45,0:03:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But could they ever grow over a meter long?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.52,0:04:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No spider species that big \Nhas ever been found.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys, I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,An idea?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The Poison Spider Investigation Team? {tankentai = exploration party; expedition team}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up. Starting today, \Nthe school's on summer break.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.38,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if a giant poisonous spider \Nis hiding somewhere in the school right now,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and multiplies while nobody's around?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.18,0:04:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows how many there'll be \Nwhen the next term starts!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.58,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're gonna find it before that happens.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sounds kinda fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's settled!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, we can come out already? {?}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the janitor just finished \Nhis rounds anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.42,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's move out.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that room was so stuffy. {lit: was suffocating}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.62,0:04:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to stay still for hours, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.62,0:05:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all that gear anyway? \NWhat'd you bring?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.52,0:05:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, time to hunt some spiders.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing weird so far.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see? There aren't any poisonous spiders.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We just started looking!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.55,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bright with the full moon tonight, \Nit's not even scary—boring, rather.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.98,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota always comes up \Nwith such childish ideas.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.42,0:05:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison Spider Investigation Team or not, \Nwhat's the point if nothing shows up? {/even if we call ourselves ...}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.92,0:05:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina-Chan, that's a bit harsh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.35,0:05:39.35,Thought,,0,0,0,,Damn it, she sure likes to run her mouth.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.18,0:05:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Ryota, isn't this the hallway \Nthey were talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.12,0:05:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, I'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.42,0:05:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing. Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I need to hit the bathroom.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.78,0:06:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.95,0:06:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Calm down, Mina-Chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all toy spiders!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.95,0:06:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I love seeing you jump like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.38,0:06:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Got your heart racing, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.72,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.72,0:06:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Manabu, seriously, that was no fair at all! {probably means "not fair that both you and mina slapped me"}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was your own fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, Ryota! {I assume she says that out loud}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, idiot, idiot, idiot! \NI'm done with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.28,0:06:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she stormed off first.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let her be.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.98,0:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What poison spiders? \NWhat monsters?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.88,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're here to scare us, \Nthen come on out already! {lit: if you're a thing that's here to come out}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{Nooo!}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.45,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Spider, inside there!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Spider!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's here... {lit: so it appeared}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No way that thing's that big!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's just call it quits.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, not after coming this far!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm waiting here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.05,0:07:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, but don't leave without us. {lit: there, don't move}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.95,0:07:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, she's so worked up she's seeing things.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.35,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Mina, there's nothing here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.02,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.18,0:07:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, you two!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.12,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.15,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.78,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.65,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Never seen a spider that big before!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, let me get a picture first! {lit: commemorative photo}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Ryota's a total monster geek. {kaiju fan}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.88,0:08:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bug spray? {殺虫剤 - insecticide}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota, get back!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more shot!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.38,0:08:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! They're scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.98,0:08:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.05,0:08:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.22,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't kill the spiders!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.12,0:09:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt them! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.15,0:09:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nthey haven't attacked Ryota at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.98,0:09:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm Sekiguchi Ryota.\N Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.22,0:09:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.15,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, is she a ghost?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.35,0:09:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.52,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.12,0:09:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.75,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.62,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the ginkgo tree.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.45,0:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginkgo tree?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! She's here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.78,0:10:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.05,0:10:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not scared of giant spiders, \Nbut ghosts freak you out? You're weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.22,0:10:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for scaring you earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not a ghost, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.98,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.52,0:10:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just hear her out.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the spirit of the ginkgo tree? {actually he says "she's the tree [itself]" meaning it's the manifestation of the soul of that particular tree}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.72,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She says showing herself to people in this form \Nis something really special.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... really wanted to save those spiders.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.42,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And what were those giant spiders?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just an illusion—\NI made them appear big with my power.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the real ones are right here. {we only see one but there was a lot earlier and idk what to choose}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Redback spider!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.68,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This one? {same}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.92,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These spider didn't come to Japan \Nbecause they wanted to. {here it's distinctly plural - -tachi}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.45,0:10:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is... {/these spiders....}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.05,0:11:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the ginkgo tree spirit, \Nwho appeared before us in her human form, {this and the following lines are kinda narration, so idk what style to choose, default, thought, or narrator}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.92,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the redback spiders in this school came all the way from Australia,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden in shipping cargo bound for Japan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.75,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But just because they're poisonous, \Npeople see them as dangerous and kill them.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.72,0:11:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The ginkgo tree felt sorry for them, \Nso she used illusions to hide them from people,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.32,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep us from getting too close.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.42,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that kinda backfired with Ryota, \Nsince he loves monsters so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.25,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,With my power, \NI can't send them back to Australia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.38,0:11:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can do is try to keep people away.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.05,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryota, can't you think of something?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave them like this. \NIt's too sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.38,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.85,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You got an idea, Manabu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask my dad for help.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.45,0:12:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he can find a way to send the spiders home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your dad might actually \Nbe able to do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.25,0:12:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginkgo Tree, I can't promise anything concrete, \Nbut I'll do my best to ask him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.55,0:12:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.18,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can I tell my dad about the spiders here?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.65,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.02,0:12:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! {/success}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take a commemorative photo together!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have a lot of cameras. {?????? no idea why but that's what she says and the camera is indeed different from before}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.18,0:12:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.25,0:12:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it broke when you collapsed. {back at 9:25}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're always like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.95,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.55,0:13:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been two months \Nsince that strange night.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.25,0:13:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With Manabu's dad's help, the redback spiders \Nwere safely returned to Australia.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.42,0:13:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, we couldn't really explain \Nwhat happened that night.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But we believe it.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe it really happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.58,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never seen the ginkgo tree take \Nhuman form again.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe someday,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.58,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,when something voiceless \Nis drowning in sorrow,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.45,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll appear before us once more. {lit: when something is sad and cannot convey it to us with words}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.15,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have a feeling about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.82,0:13:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so how was it? \NThe spider story.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You weren't scared? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.05,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Then next story is about meeting Hanako-san! {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hanako-san}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.22,0:13:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, Episode 2, \N{\i1}The Story About Hanako-sa{\i0}n, begins!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, you do it like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.38,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.25,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And then this part goes here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Done! All set!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.35,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Manabu-kun, \Nyou really know how to use a computer!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just watched my dad use one for work \Nand thought it looked fun,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so I started messing around with it and picked it up.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.68,0:14:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wow. / Oh?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ryota, you're being obnoxious.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.85,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, class is finally over, \Nso why are we still studying? That's boring!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.02,0:14:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't studying!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's online communication! {/computer}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use the phone line \Nto talk to all sorts of people
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.65,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and see tons of information!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.68,0:14:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to look up stuff about music.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,See? That's still studying.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.78,0:15:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's sports info too, \Nlike your favorite soccer and baseball.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.55,0:15:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And anime and games too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.05,0:15:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.78,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've said that sooner!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, for today, let's choose... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Sky Network?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.55,0:15:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a network made \Nfor elementary school kids like us.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we're connected!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where should we go first?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Sports, sports!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check out music!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.35,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.62,0:15:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now. \NHow about a compromise: sci-fi!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.92,0:15:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.95,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this "Mystery Club"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.45,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... I've never been there before either.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.42,0:15:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, is this a scary story thing? {think he means "a collection of creepy urban myths", like on TV or in printed press}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ryota, you scared?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Of course not!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.78,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.08,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Legend of the Slit-Mouthed Woman? {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kuchisake-onna}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Curse of the Human-Faced Dog? {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japanese_urban_legends#Jinmenken_(%22Human-Faced_Dog%22)}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystery of the Science Lab? {seems to be relatively new, doesn't have a wiki}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.75,0:16:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.18,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.52,0:16:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay? You look pale.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Past of Hanako-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Hanako-san who appears if you knock on the bathroom door three times.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna see that one, Mina-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.98,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.48,0:17:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"It happened more than ten years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.02,0:17:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain incident at a school in northern Japan \Nwas the start of the Hanako-san rumor. {touhoku}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.72,0:17:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl who went to that school
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.35,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was bullied over and over by her classmates.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One winter day, while she \Nwas locked in the bathroom,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.42,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,snow piled up so high that the roof collapsed.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.15,0:17:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trapped underneath \Nthe snow and debris, the girl died.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl became Hanako-san,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.78,0:17:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and to take revenge on those who bullied her, \Nshe began appearing in school bathrooms,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.95,0:17:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,dragging anyone she met\N into the world of the dead."
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.48,0:17:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of a sad story.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but remember what it said later on?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.32,0:17:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a boy named Jiro \Nwho always stood up for her.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.58,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he transferred away \Nsoon after, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.85,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Hanako-san still appears in the bathroom \Nbecause she wants to see Jiro again?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.88,0:18:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's just a rumor. \NWho cares?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.95,0:18:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, if it's true, it's kind of sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.25,0:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if it's revenge instead? Then what?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.88,0:18:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Ryota, what are we doing today?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna keep going with the online thing? {/computer communication}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.22,0:18:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sounds good. \NIt's Saturday anyway, we've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're hooked now too, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.28,0:18:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry, I've got some \Nfamily stuff to take care of.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it go. It's just family stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was kind of dull.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't feel right without Mina. {lit: the aftertaste is bad - w/e that means}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's up with her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.62,0:19:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She was acting strange earlier.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know—let's stop by her place.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.95,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But she said she had errands, didn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.85,0:19:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she's going back to school \Nto get something she forgot?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.02,0:19:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina went back to meet Hanako-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What? But that's just an old rumor!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.38,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone logged into \NBlue Sky Network right after us.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be Mina.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.45,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell where she went?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.25,0:20:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.45,0:20:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"On a day of red sunset, \Nin the second-floor girls' restroom
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.75,0:20:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,bathed in the evening light, open the door as the school's closing melody plays." {gekou = leaving school (at the end of the day); getting out of school}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.15,0:20:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The school's closing melody...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,just started! {gekou}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.55,0:20:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.58,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-san, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for a boy, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.68,0:21:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy's name... it's Jiro, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.18,0:22:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Jiro-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.88,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I learned all sorts of stuff about you \Nthrough the computer network.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.28,0:22:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Hanako-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.82,0:22:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your death happened a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.85,0:22:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So even if Jiro's still alive, \Nhe'd be an adult by now, and you...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.88,0:22:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Jiro-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.95,0:22:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.32,0:22:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Jiro-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.78,0:22:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, Jiro-kun's already... {an adult}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.72,0:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.45,0:22:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you let me see Jiro-kun?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.28,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.65,0:22:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all terrible!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:53.25,0:22:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You bullied me and laughed about it! {/took joy in it}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.85,0:23:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you! \NI'll never forgive anyone who hurt me!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.92,0:23:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.25,0:23:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.85,0:23:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.28,0:23:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.35,0:23:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.15,0:23:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here to bully me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.05,0:23:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.82,0:23:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.22,0:23:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mina, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.62,0:23:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Ryota?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:40.48,0:23:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just panic—think of something! {lit: don't ask me what to do}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.55,0:23:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a professor's kid, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's got nothing to do with this! {lit: even if you say so}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:54.68,0:23:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just die for all I care. {??????? can't hear shit but I want to think I hear something about kutabare there}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.65,0:24:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send anyone who bullies me \Nstraight to the other world!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.42,0:24:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is an idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.52,0:24:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a coward!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.75,0:24:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a dimwit! {?????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.68,0:24:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a dummy! \NJiro is a blockhead! {manuke / otankonasu}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.05,0:24:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a crybaby!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:19.52,0:24:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a mommy's boy! {?????? maybe "mother's crybaby"?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.65,0:24:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a coward! \NJiro is a cheat! {bit liar}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:26.48,0:24:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro is a weakling! {ikujinashi}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.95,0:24:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro's... uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:31.08,0:24:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:34.35,0:24:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who badmouthed Jiro-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.45,0:24:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.25,0:24:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive that.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive anyone who speaks ill of Jiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.02,0:24:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you too—\Nto the other side with that girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.45,0:24:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got it all backward! {lit: we're the ones who won't forgive you}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.18,0:25:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That girl, Mina wasn't mocking you! \NShe was trying to help you find Jiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.32,0:25:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump her in with the ones who hurt you!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:11.45,0:25:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it! Don't you dare take her away, ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:15.15,0:25:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't ever let you!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:25.68,0:25:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You like that girl, don't you? {/love}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:31.25,0:25:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:34.15,0:25:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I can't stand seeing \Nsomeone innocent suffer for nothing, that's all.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.55,0:25:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.18,0:25:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that girl's Jiro-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.62,0:25:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to protect her?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.58,0:25:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.85,0:25:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.98,0:25:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:01.68,0:26:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:03.72,0:26:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I won't be taking her.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.98,0:26:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.98,0:26:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:08.18,0:26:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But promise me
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.92,0:26:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that you'll keep protecting her.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:14.52,0:26:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! I promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:18.55,0:26:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:24.88,0:26:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:27.98,0:26:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:29.58,0:26:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryota!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:32.18,0:26:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:34.45,0:26:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:44.78,0:26:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how our strange encounter with Hanako-san came to an end.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:50.18,0:26:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that day, none of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:51.95,0:26:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, rather, not a single person \Nat school has seen her again.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.58,0:27:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check out the soccer network today!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:00.02,0:27:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No way—music!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.38,0:27:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Soccer!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:03.02,0:27:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Music!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.32,0:27:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be soccer!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:06.28,0:27:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's music, obviously!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.12,0:27:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you two give it a rest already?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:14.85,0:27:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:16.05,0:27:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it snowing in here?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:18.72,0:27:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:27:19.75,0:27:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet it's Hanako-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:23.28,0:27:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's telling us not to fight.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:26.25,0:27:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she ever found Jiro-kun.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:30.48,0:27:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.25,0:27:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{chapter}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:51.88,0:27:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad that Mina-chan \Nwasn't taken away?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:55.45,0:27:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And Ryota, for someone who hates ghosts, \Nhe sure held his ground.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:59.82,0:28:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Hanako-san gets to see \NJiro-kun again someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:05.35,0:28:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And that wraps up today's story.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:08.72,0:28:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for watching till the end, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:11.45,0:28:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can all meet again someday, somewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:15.55,0:28:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, be careful \Nabout what you encounter at school.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:20.08,0:28:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that strange rumor everyone's whispering about \Nmight just be true, like the one we've just seen.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:27.85,0:28:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's all for now. Bye bye!
